packageDescription.name: Show Message (Script) Extension
packageDescription.author: Kino Rose
packageDescription.description: This extension adds the ability to use JavaScript in a new show message (script) command. Format currency, show emojis, format numbers, and write some plain old JavaScript. Emoji short codes similar to those in Discord. Example: :smile:
packageDescription.license:
This extension is free for non-commercial and commercial use. 

Credit with: EIS - Kino
